WE ALSO HAD
OUR SPECIAL EFFECTS PEOPLE

26:14.050 --> 26:17.010
THROWING RUBBER GLASS
THROUGH THE WINDOW.

26:17.053 --> 26:19.142
THROUGH THE USE
OF PHYSICAL MODELS

26:19.186 --> 26:21.710
AND THINGS THAT ARE CREATED
ENTIRELY IN THE COMPUTER,

26:21.754 --> 26:23.712
HE WAS ABLE TO CREATE
THAT WORLD.

