[Elan] WE HAD FANS GOING,

26:25.366 --> 26:27.629
LOTS AND LOTS OF BITS
AND PIECES.

26:27.673 --> 26:30.023
[Olivia] THERE'S THAT MOMENT
WHERE AMBER--

26:30.066 --> 26:33.504
IT'S THE POINT OF IMPACT
WHEN THE BUS WAS HIT,

26:33.548 --> 26:35.158
AND HER BODY
GOING FORWARD--

26:35.202 --> 26:37.639
I THOUGHT THAT
WAS EXTRAORDINARY.

26:47.649 --> 26:57.616
♪♪♪

26:57.659 --> 27:07.626
♪♪♪

27:07.669 --> 27:11.412
