28:13.561 --> 28:15.781
WE'D COME RIGHT TO THE END.

28:23.963 --> 28:27.531
DOWNTOWN SOMEWHERE IN L.A.

28:27.575 --> 28:30.143
I HAVE NO CLUE WHERE I'M AT.

28:31.971 --> 28:33.494
THESE ARE THE LAST DAYS.

28:33.537 --> 28:37.193
♪♪♪

28:41.284 --> 28:43.852
THERE ARE SO MANY
DIFFERENT LAYERS TO THE SHOW.

