THAT WAS DRAWN ON A MONDAY,

30:03.366 --> 30:05.542
BUILT ON A TUESDAY, AND ACTED ON
ON A WEDNESDAY

30:05.586 --> 30:08.850
IS JUST MIND-BENDING.THIS SHOW BELONGS
TO ALL OF US,

30:08.894 --> 30:11.592
AND IT'S SOMETHING
I'M EXTRAORDINARILY PROUD OF.

30:15.726 --> 30:18.381
THREE, TWO, ONE!

30:18.425 --> 30:21.341
[cheering]

30:23.909 --> 30:27.347
♪♪♪

30:49.412 --> 30:53.025
SO THIS IS IT.
