OF PEOPLE AROUND THE WORLD...AROUND THE WORLD.

36:12.126 --> 36:14.215
ARE INVESTED IN THE CHARACTER
OF GREGORY HOUSE.

36:14.259 --> 36:17.131
I THINK IT'S BECAUSE
OF YOUR BLUE EYES.

36:17.175 --> 36:19.089
RIGHT.

36:19.133 --> 36:21.179
I THINK THAT'S IT.THAT'S PRETTY MUCH
WHAT I WAS SAYING,

36:21.222 --> 36:22.745
BUT MORE CONDENSED.

36:22.789 --> 36:26.140
♪♪♪

36:29.839 --> 36:31.798
