37:12.099 --> 37:14.971
THANK YOU, "HOUSE."THANK YOU FOR EIGHT
GREAT SEASONS.

37:15.015 --> 37:16.843
THANK YOU.THANK YOU.

37:16.886 --> 37:20.281
I KNOW I AM NEVER,
EVER GOING TO FORGET IT.

